<plot>Darren McAree is James Hadley in Andrew Davidson's unforgettable tale of guilt, disillusionment, and fear. Hadley arrives at a station in a whirlwind of terror and bewilderment, fleeing from a troubled past that threatens to reappear and turn his world upside down. Along the way, a chance encounter with the mysterious Lara forces Hadley into an emotional reckoning, facing up to everything that he has come to fear. 'Autumn Heart' is a poignant and powerful exploration of love, loss and what's left behind.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?052158</url></doc>
